description:
Does the Biblical account of a worldwide flood match the evidence in the geological column? This lecture discusses the ice ages and reasons for mammalian distribution and appearance in the upper portion of the geological column. The evolution of humans and the time constraints in terms of recolonization of post-flood Earth are also discussed.
